SimpleLion - A simple, multi-language localization framework.

This is the Ruby-specific SimpleLion module.

Project tracking and basic information: http://redmine.phitherek.mooo.com/projects/simplelion
Documentation for the module: http://phitherek.mooo.com/rdoc/simplelion-ruby/SimpleLion.html
Coverage for the module: http://phitherek.mooo.com/coverage/simplelion-ruby/

Installation - add to your Gemfile:
gem 'simplelion-ruby'
or run:
gem install simplelion-ruby

Usage:
require 'simplelion-ruby'
